\[\mathbf{S}_{m,i}(\boldsymbol{\ell}^{\sharp})=\{\boldsymbol{\ell}^{\sharp}_{i} \}_{j=1}^{m}\]

_for_

\[\boldsymbol{\ell}^{\sharp}_{j}=\boldsymbol{c}+\frac{-m+2j-1}{m}\boldsymbol{g} _{i}\epsilon_{i}+\sum_{j\neq i}\boldsymbol{g}_{j}\epsilon_{j}\]

